<h1>Welcome to MarkdownToRazor</h1>

<p>This is a Blazor Server application that demonstrates build-time code generation for converting Markdown files to
    Razor pages.</p>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Build-time markdown to Razor page conversion</li>
    <li>YAML frontmatter support for custom routing and metadata</li>
    <li>Automatic route generation</li>
    <li>FluentUI integration</li>
    <li>Syntax highlighting with copy functionality</li>
</ul>

